questions.question:
You are given a class Entity defined as follows:
class Entity { type: file | directory; size: // if it is a file; EntityIds: // list of child Entity IDs if it is a directory };
You are provided with multiple Entity IDs, where each Entity can either be a file or a directory. If it is a file, its size will be given. If it is a directory, you will be given the Entity IDs of its children. You need to implement a function that, given an Entity ID, returns the total size of that Entity.
